title: Mister Monk
description:
DOWNLOAD

Mister Monk is New Age/Spiritual album.

The album is dedicated to the soul searchers of past, present and future; and all music lovers who love the sound of sound.
With a running time of 25 minutes, 48 seconds, Mister Monk has five tracks that span the consciousness stages of a monk, or any person in quest of the source of eternal bliss and the ultimate truth.

The tracks

01 - Shoonya
02 - Yatra
03 - Oorja
04 - Dhvani
05 - Oas
